  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, as vividly as today, my father was ill at that time in bed, and he asked me I should board the train to Trebisov, to that city where that happened, and try to sit in the back of the train to see what's going to happen with my two brothers, with my sister.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow they got-- we got notified that they were captured.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was, as a matter of fact, on that train as they brought them back to Michalovce.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were at that time still a little bit ashamed for the public, so they did not have a march from the train station through the front of the city, rather than through a back way towards the jail.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was at a distance of about maybe 50 or 100 feet, trailing them so I should be able to tell my parents that's-- what's happening.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they brought them to a place where the jail was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of, course, they all locked them up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I ran home quickly to tell my parents what I saw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father tried, through different channels, through people that he knew during all the all years that he was there, to try to get them released.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was of no avail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's towards, the-- I would say towards the end of March-- maybe about, I would say around the 20th, or so-- they took them away from jail, both my two brothers and my sister.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they carried them away, I did not know where-- at least for awhile.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they disappeared, period.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
